g.cust_coupon

Interface Cust_couponDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Cust_CoupnDBDAO

    public interface Cust_couponDAO
    This class represents the methods relevant to the join table: Customer-coupon. These methods will be overwritten to allow interface with the relevant Database/file. In this case we are interfacing with Derby DB.
